{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/Welcome_.png?t=1733137133\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Of Ash and Steel</strong> is an immersive third-person open-world RPG created by a passionate team that values the essence of classic old-school RPGs and modern designs. Explore the lands of a once-prosperous island, hone your combat skills, and survive in the unforgiving realm of the Kingdom of the Seven. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/Master_The_Art_Of_Combat.png?t=1733137133\" />Learn to stand up for yourself using different combat stances, environments, and active skills. Tailor your fighting style to suit you, from the agile rapier wielder to a heavy armour-clad knight, or create something unique! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/GIF_Combat.gif?t=1733137133\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/Shape_the_fate_of_the_world.png?t=1733137133\" />Gain strength, survive, and forge alliances. Prove that even someone who has lost everything can become a significant force that can shape the fate of the whole island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/GIF_Dialog.gif?t=1733137133\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/Explore_like_you_used_to_.png?t=1733137133\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Of Ash and Steel has no marker system, and quests won't lead you by the hand. Rediscover the joy of exploration and let curiosity be your guide; the world promises rich rewards for those who dare to uncover its secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/GIF_Walking_v2.gif?t=1733137133\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733137133","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/page.bg.jpg?t=1733137133","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/39aa77af1ae8ffc745cc837f1824016a8208627a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733137133","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/39aa77af1ae8ffc745cc837f1824016a8208627a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733137133","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/Welcome_.png?t=1733137133\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Of Ash and Steel</strong> is an immersive third-person open-world RPG created by a passionate team that values the essence of classic old-school RPGs and modern designs. Explore the lands of a once-prosperous island, hone your combat skills, and survive in the unforgiving realm of the Kingdom of the Seven. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893820/extras/Master_The_Art_Of_Combat.png?t=1733137133\"